            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                Hic requiescit in <lb n="2"/>pace vir venera<lb break="no" n="3"/>bil&amp;lt;i=E&amp;gt;s Ludubertus <lb n="4"/>de nobile genere qui <lb n="5"/>vix<surplus>x</surplus>it ann&amp;lt;o=U&amp;gt;s plus <lb n="6"/>minus LXV cuius de<lb break="no" n="7"/>posi&amp;lt;t=C&amp;gt;io eius est XVI <lb n="8"/>K<expan><ex>a</ex><abbr>l</abbr><ex>endas</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Ian</abbr><ex>uarias</ex></expan> et o<expan><ex>m</ex><abbr>nes</abbr></expan> res suas <lb n="9"/>s<expan><ex>an</ex><abbr>c</abbr><ex>t</ex><abbr>o</abbr></expan> Petro trade<lb break="no" n="10"/>dit et se <expan><abbr>clericu</abbr><ex>m</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>feci</abbr><ex>t</ex></expan> 
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Tag der Beisetzung war 17 Dezember.</p>
            </div>
